<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Reinstated</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5cb85c; }
        .content p { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Account Reinstated
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Good news! Your Amora Hub account has been reinstated and is now active.</p>
            <p>We appreciate your cooperation and encourage you to review our community guidelines to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for everyone.</p>
            <p>Welcome back!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Amora Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>